Condo Cops tells the real-life stories of people that do the most outrageous things, while property managers do their best to enforce the condo association's Rules and Regulations. Filmed locally – this reality show is sure to showcase the unusual happenings daily at condos around the Tampa Bay Area. The show premiers Sunday, October 25th at 4:30 PM, on CW Television Network (Tampa Bay area only). Brighthouse: Ch 4 – Direct TV: Ch 44.
